<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, 
		initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body
    style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
    padding: 50px;
 font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">
    <div style="color: #374151; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; text-align: left;">
        <p>Hey there, <%=name%>
        </p>
        <p>We hope you're as excited as we are because Memeland's newest sensation is about to rock the internet! 🌐
        </p>
        <p>🎥 Attached video for your exclusive welcome
          
        </p>
        <p>We're bursting with gratitude as we gear up to welcome you on board in just 3 days—mark your calendars for
            <%=formattedTargetDate%>! 🗓️

        </p>

        <p>Onboarding with us isn't just another day at the office; it's an adventure waiting to happen! 🚀
          
        </p>
        <p>
            The Memeland awaits, and we can't wait to show you the ropes.

        </p>
        <p>Stay tuned for the memes, the magic, and the mayhem!

        </p>
        
        <p>
          <b>
          Warm regards,<br/>
          Human Resources
        </b>
          </p>


          <p>
            <a href="https://storage.googleapis.com/jarvis-dev-bucket/3 Days to go!!! (3) (1).mp4" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none;">
                <img src="https://example.com/path-to-thumbnail.jpg" alt=" Please Click on Attachment to see video" style="width:100%; max-width:600px;">
            </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        let name = '<%-name%>'
        let heading = document
            .getElementById('text_from_script');

        heading.innerText = name;
        name = "Mr/Mrs. " + name;
        let heading_man = document.getElementById(
            'text_from_script_manipulated');
        heading_man.innerText = name; 
    </script>
</body>

</html>